The paper discusses the storage and distribution of virtual machine images in federated cloud models, which involves concepts related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and networking (cs.NI). It also touches upon quality of service (QoS) which falls under the category of computer communication (cs.CC). The paper also discusses various systems and their comparison, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper identifies current limitations, challenges, and open trends, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
